                  "revisionId": 2789467,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The Weak Point Damage is multiplicative with bonuses to Headshot Multiplier, such as from Secondary Deadhead ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
